reviewText: My boyfriend has many issues of "PLAYBOY" back to August 1956 and also has 89 movies from that magazine. I am Chinese, so I am interested in seeing Asian Playmates. This video has the September 1992 Playmate Morena Corwin whose mother is Korean, so she is the main girl I wanted to see in it. My boyfriend also likes Vanessa Gleason Miss September 1998. The other girls in it are attractive, but we prefer Morena and Vanessa to Donna D'Errico and the Dutch Van Breeschooten twins. It is nice to see about fifteen minutes of Morena Corwin in this video. I have found some more "Playmate Profile" videos with Asian Playmates. My boyfriend already had some, but I found this video and more in the series at Amazon.
